df-cmp
blocks.content: Definition of a compact topology. A topology is compact iff any open covering of its underlying set contains a finite subcovering (Heine-Borel property). Definition C''' of [BourbakiTop1] p. I.59. Note: Bourbaki uses the term "quasi-compact" but it is not the modern usage (which we follow). (Contributed by FL, 22-Dec-2008.)

blocks.content: The predicate "is a compact topology". (Contributed by FL, 22-Dec-2008.) (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 11-Feb-2015.)

thm iscmp(setvar s0, setvar s1, class c0, class c1) {
  |- wb(wcel(c0, ccmp), wa(wcel(c0, ctop), wral(s0, cpw(c0), wi(wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s1))))))))
  -| wceq(c1, cuni(c0))
  -| diffss(s0, s1)
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s1, c0)
} = {
  elrab2(hs0, c0, ccmp, ctop, wral(s0, cpw(c0), wi(wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s1)))))), wral(s0, cpw(cv(hs0)), wi(wceq(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s1)))))))
  raleqbidv(s0, cpw(cv(hs0)), cpw(c0), wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wi(wceq(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s1))))), wi(wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s1))))))
  pweq(cv(hs0), c0)
  imbi12d(wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wceq(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s1)))), wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s1)))))
  eqeq1d(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s0)), c1, wceq(cv(hs0), c0))
  rexbidv(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wceq(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s1))), wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s1))))
  eqeq1d(cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(cv(s1)), c1, wceq(cv(hs0), c0))
  syl6eqr(cuni(cv(hs0)), c1, cuni(c0), wceq(cv(hs0), c0))
  unieq(cv(hs0), c0)
  df-cmp(hs0, s0, s1)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(ctop)
  diff.hs0.w(wral(s0, cpw(c0), wi(wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s0))), wrex(s1, cin(cpw(cv(s0)), cfn), wceq(c1, cuni(cv(s1)))))))
  diff.wceq.s(s0, cv(hs0), c0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.wceq.s(s1, cv(hs0), c0)
  diff.cv.s(s1, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s1, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.s(s1)
}

  ‚ä£ c1 = ‚ãÉ c0

  pweq(hs0, c0)

  eqeq1d(‚ãÉ hs0, ‚ãÉ s0, c1, hs0 = c0)
  rexbidv(s1, (P(s0)‚ãÇ Fin), hs0 = c0, ‚ãÉ hs0 = ‚ãÉ s1, c1 = ‚ãÉ s1)
  eqeq1d(‚ãÉ hs0, ‚ãÉ s1, c1, hs0 = c0)

blocks.name: cmpcov
blocks.content: An open cover of a compact topology has a finite subcover. (Contributed by Jeff Hankins, 29-Jun-2009.)
blocks.origin:
thm cmpcov(setvar s0, class c0, class c1, class c2) {
  |- wi(w3a(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, c0), wceq(c2, cuni(c1))), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(c1), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0)))))
  -| wceq(c2, cuni(c0))
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s0, c1)
} = {
  3impia(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, c0), wceq(c2, cuni(c1)), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(c1), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0)))))
  rspcdva(hs0, c1, cpw(c0), wa(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, c0)), wi(wceq(c2, cuni(c1)), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(c1), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0))))), wi(wceq(c2, cuni(cv(hs0))), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(cv(hs0)), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0))))))
  imbi12d(wceq(cv(hs0), c1), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(hs0))), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(cv(hs0)), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0)))), wceq(c2, cuni(c1)), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(c1), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0)))))
  eqeq2d(c2, cuni(cv(hs0)), cuni(c1), wceq(cv(hs0), c1))
  unieq(cv(hs0), c1)
  rexeqdv(s0, cin(cpw(cv(hs0)), cfn), cin(cpw(c1), cfn), wceq(cv(hs0), c1), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0))))
  ineq1d(cpw(cv(hs0)), cfn, cpw(c1), wceq(cv(hs0), c1))
  pweq(cv(hs0), c1)
  adantr(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, c0), wral(hs0, cpw(c0), wi(wceq(c2, cuni(cv(hs0))), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(cv(hs0)), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0)))))))
  simprbi(wcel(c0, ccmp), wral(hs0, cpw(c0), wi(wceq(c2, cuni(cv(hs0))), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(cv(hs0)), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0)))))), wcel(c0, ctop))
  iscmp(hs0, s0, c0, c2)
  elpwd(c1, c0, universe, wa(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, c0)))
  ancoms(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, c0), wcel(c1, universe))
  ssexg(c1, c0, ccmp)
  simpr(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, c0))
  diff.hs0.c(c1)
  diff.hs0.c(cpw(c0))
  diff.hs0.w(wi(wceq(c2, cuni(c1)), wrex(s0, cin(cpw(c1), cfn), wceq(c2, cuni(cv(s0))))))
  diff.cin.s(s0, cpw(cv(hs0)), cfn)
  diff.cpw.s(s0, cv(hs0))
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.cin.s(s0, cpw(c1), cfn)
  diff.cpw.s(s0, c1)
  diff.cfn.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
}

  diff.cin.s(s0, P(hs0), cfn)
  diff.cpw.s(s0, hs0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)

  diff.cpw.s(s0, c1)
  diff.cfn.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)

}

blocks.name: tgcmp
blocks.content: A topology generated by a basis is compact iff open covers drawn from the basis have finite subcovers. (See also ~ alexsub , which further specializes to subbases, assuming the ultrafilter lemma.) (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 26-Aug-2015.)

blocks.name: cmpfii
blocks.content: In a compact topology, a system of closed sets with nonempty finite intersections has a nonempty intersection. (Contributed by Stefan O'Rear, 22-Feb-2015.)
blocks.origin:
thm cmpfii(class c0, class c1) {
  |- wi(w3a(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, cfv(ccld, c0)), wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, c1)))), wne(cint(c1), emptycls))
} = {
  3impia(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, cfv(ccld, c0)), wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, c1))), wne(cint(c1), emptycls))
  syl2anr(wcel(c0, ccmp), wss(c1, cfv(ccld, c0)), wi(wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, c1))), wne(cint(c1), emptycls)), wcel(c1, cpw(cfv(ccld, c0))), wral(hs0, cpw(cfv(ccld, c0)), wi(wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, cv(hs0)))), wne(cint(cv(hs0)), emptycls))))
  biimpri(wss(c1, cfv(ccld, c0)), wcel(c1, cpw(cfv(ccld, c0))))
  elpw2(c1, cfv(ccld, c0))
  fvex(ccld, c0)
  ibi(wcel(c0, ccmp), wral(hs0, cpw(cfv(ccld, c0)), wi(wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, cv(hs0)))), wne(cint(cv(hs0)), emptycls))))
  syl(wcel(c0, ccmp), wb(wcel(c0, ccmp), wral(hs0, cpw(cfv(ccld, c0)), wi(wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, cv(hs0)))), wne(cint(cv(hs0)), emptycls)))), wcel(c0, ctop))
  cmptop(c0)
  cmpfi(hs0, c0)
  rspcva(hs0, c1, cpw(cfv(ccld, c0)), wi(wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, cv(hs0)))), wne(cint(cv(hs0)), emptycls)), wi(wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, c1))), wne(cint(c1), emptycls)))
  imbi12d(wceq(cv(hs0), c1), wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, cv(hs0)))), wne(cint(cv(hs0)), emptycls), wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, c1))), wne(cint(c1), emptycls))
  notbid(wceq(cv(hs0), c1), wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, cv(hs0))), wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, c1)))
  eleq2d(emptycls, cfv(cfi, cv(hs0)), cfv(cfi, c1), wceq(cv(hs0), c1))
  fveq2(cv(hs0), c1, cfi)
  neeq1d(cint(cv(hs0)), emptycls, cint(c1), wceq(cv(hs0), c1))
  inteq(cv(hs0), c1)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(c1)
  diff.hs0.c(cpw(cfv(ccld, c0)))
  diff.hs0.w(wi(wn(wcel(emptycls, cfv(cfi, c1))), wne(cint(c1), emptycls)))
}
